{"tid":1869250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名美國人及一名日本人因感染新型冠狀病毒　在武漢逝世","createTime":"2020-02-08T05:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T07:38:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2d8eb794f2680d406017192ca7ff80f1c19653","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:35:10.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】2月8日新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情消息一覽：<br />\n<br />\n最新：(1310)<br />\n<br />\n一名美國人及一名日本人因感染新型冠狀病毒，在武漢逝世。<br />\n<br />\n寶瓶星號郵輪抵達台灣基隆港，25名衛生人員登船檢疫，料需五小時。若有人對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陽性反應，全船乘客及船員須留船檢疫14日。<br />\n<br />\n北京出現第二宗死亡個案。<br />\n<br />\n湖北醫院開始出現氧氣供應不足，影響呼吸機使用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379793&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=1047f670\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379793&h=667ce7a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379793</a>"},{"pid":"26363e5f6c3f7a1d1316f141568e7745709933d9","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"2月7日本港出入境旅客數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGzzvmq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGzzvmq.jpg&h=e2bf6f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2月6日本港出入境旅客數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GRRxz3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GRRxz3.jpg&h=5cf9904b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 深圳灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4ab51aa9cd8a901786dda8d3748b2312f5bcbe","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26363e5f6c3f7a1d1316f141568e7745709933d9","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"2月7日本港出入境旅客數字<br />\n<img src=\"htt