me":"2020-02-08T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"港澳其他消息：<br />\n本港累計26宗確診個案，最新確診的58歲男患者於珠海和澳門工作。<br />\n<br />\n即日起抵港者若14日內曾到內地須強制檢疫，違例可被罰款及監禁。深圳灣口岸早上人流疏落。<br />\n<br />\n港航一班北京來港航班因延誤至凌晨抵港，全機乘客須強制檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局：部分防疫裝備只餘一個月存量。"},{"pid":"facef8f8b18bd4317eeca76bd2c0ddbc6f1deac8","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"醫學會會長何仲平建議規管市民求診時作健康申報。<br />\n<br />\n內地入境強制檢疫措施生效前，昨日有95982人次入境，較前一日增17%。入境人次八成是香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n內地出入境管理局要求相關部門昨日起，暫停辦理內地居民赴港商務簽注。"},{"pid":"f563b1489d44b9e1afc08dbc97114e4953dfe144","tid":1869250,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔知班港豬係武漢情況點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c127a067f655b5fa5a3abbb7b239a9d6c53a3840","tid":1869250,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"NY Times 話係六十歲女美帝子民<br />\n<br />\n有長期病"},{"pid":"86f92ffd1b1027fb71344cfcaf95baa28a1549ef","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5ef0a184cc491d6320965ff71e3f261c85128a5","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"武漢市入院中的60歲男性日本人死亡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1869161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1869161</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"日本第一個死亡case<br />\n竟然客死異鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fe853f4a46f89b8851783b369e63a559ad4f54","tid":1869250,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c127a067f655b5fa5a3abbb7b239a9d6c53a3840","tid":1869250,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"NY Times 話係六十歲女美帝子民<br />\n<br />\n有長期病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{